      <title>加密货币亿万富翁 Brian Armstrong 取消捐赠承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/coinbase-billionaire-brian-armstrong-removed-from-giving-pledge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 的首席执行官布莱恩·阿姆斯特朗 (Brian Armstrong) 上周被取消了“捐赠誓言”的资格，该誓言是亿万富翁的承诺，他们承诺在有生之年或立下遗嘱时将大部分财富捐献给慈善机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/coinbase-billionaire-brian-armstrong-removed-from-giving-pledge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 21:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
